{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place a large bowl on mixing bowl lid and weigh in clams. Remove bowl, cover clams with water then add salt. Leave to soak for approx. 2 hours to release the sand. After this time, drain clams in Varoma dish and set aside.","Place oil in mixing bowl and heat <nobr>3 min\/120°C\/speed 1<\/nobr>.","Add garlic, chop <nobr>5 sec\/speed 5<\/nobr> then sauté <nobr>5 min\/120°C\/speed 2<\/nobr>.","Add mustard, water and wine. Place covered Varoma with clams into position and steam <nobr>20 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<\/nobr>.","Transfer clams to a serving dish, drizzle with sauce and garnish with coriander before serving hot."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["1000 g venus clams","2 tsp fine sea salt","70 g olive oil","6 garlic cloves, large","15 g mustard","150 g water, plus extra for soaking","15 g white wine","fresh coriander leaves, roughly chopped, for garnishing"]}],"id":"r384564","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-oiwZsqKh3fs\/XZWZYYgzdsI\/AAAAAAAAeMA\/FQwieUbcSL8IMV6QQDS40knWhcKyvUfvACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_aDry4n2ZL3o11QgL.png","title":"Clams with Garlic Sauce","publishedAt":"2018-07-30T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"24 g","fat":"19 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"7 g","calories":"1272 kJ \/ 304 kcal"},"usefulItems":"large bowl","basicInfo":["easy","10m","2h 40m","4 portions"]}